{"tid":482164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋尋覓覓冷冷清清 一個悲慘嘅愛情故事","createTime":"2017-11-28T02:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T02:10:25.000Z","uid":147519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd0ad2b82570e96ae6c7043022717b811995f94","tid":482164,"uid":147519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"<del><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/101013_89853b7b91bd860a8e8524d2a67b82f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F101013_89853b7b91bd860a8e8524d2a67b82f6.jpg&h=f85d9510&s={SIZE}\" /></del><br />\n是咁的<br />\n等巴士嗰陣<br />\n有個男人行緊去我隔離線排隊<br />\n經過我身邊突然擰轉面大聲喊：<br />\n「有車喇BB！」<br />\n本身以為佢女朋友同佢一齊搭車<br />\n點知<br />\n由始至終都喺得佢一個<br />\n我望住佢孤獨嘅背影<br />\n黯然神傷"}]}